            bindings = <
&kp GRAVE  &kp C_VOLUME_DOWN  &kp C_VOLUME_UP  &kp K_MUTE  &trans  &trans  &trans  &kp SYSREQ  &trans         &trans    &kp UP_ARROW  &trans  &trans
